<div id="item15819843" class="journal-entry">

  <div class="journal-entry-float-day"><span class="name">Thursday</span></div><div class="journal-entry-float-date"><span class="month">Apr</span><span class="date">12</span><span class="year">2012</span></div>
  
  
  
  <div class="journal-entry-text">
  
      
      <h2 class="title">
    
        
    
        <a class="journal-entry-navigation-current" href="/recipes/2012/4/12/white-asparagus-bruschetta.html">White Asparagus&nbsp;Bruschetta</a>  
     
         
    
      </h2>
      
      

    
  
      
      <div class="body">
  
        
        
        
          <p>Spring is here! On our recent trip to the farmers market we could feel the change of the season in the air. Vibrant colors and new varieties of produce have begun to fill the market place once again.</p>
<p>A light lunch inspired by spring blooms combines rustic bread with sweet, crisp flavors of white asparagus and creamy ricotta.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Styling Assistant: <a href="http://www.hannahschmitz.de/">Hannah Schmitz</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://thejewelsofny.squarespace.com/asparagus-bruschetta/">get recipe &gt;</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/storage/Spring_Bruschetta.jpg?__SQUARESPACE_CACHEVERSION=1334268011988" alt="" /></p>

        
  
          
  
         
  
      </div>

    

  </div>

  
  
  <div class="clearer"></div>

</div>
</div>







<div class="journal-entry-wrapper post-text authored-by-thejewelsofny ">
<div id="item15706434" class="journal-entry">

  <div class="journal-entry-float-day"><span class="name">Tuesday</span></div><div class="journal-entry-float-date"><span class="month">Apr</span><span class="date">03</span><span class="year">2012</span></div>
  
  
  
  <div class="journal-entry-text">
  
      
      <h2 class="title">
    
        
    
        <a class="journal-entry-navigation-current" href="/recipes/2012/4/3/crispy-roast-chicken-and-shallots-with-miso-gravy.html">Crispy Roast Chicken and Shallots with Miso&nbsp;Gravy</a>  
     
         
    
      </h2>
      
      

    
  
      
      <div class="body">
  
        
        
        
          <p>We recently worked with <a href="http://www.foodandwine.com/recipes/crispy-roast-chicken-and-shallots-with-miso-gravy">Food &amp; Wine</a> to style their delicious cripsy roast chicken with fresh herbs and a buttery, shallot miso gravy. This dish is perfect for a weeknight dinner, paired with a glass of a full-bodied, fruity Chardonnay.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Styling Assistant: <a href="http://www.hannahschmitz.de/">Hannah Schmitz</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/crispy-roast-chicken-and-shall/">get recipe &gt;</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="full-image-block ssNonEditable"><span><img src="/storage/RoastChicken_2.jpg?__SQUARESPACE_CACHEVERSION=1333468895306" alt="" /></span></span></p>

        
  
          
  
         
  
      </div>

    

  </div>

  
  
  <div class="clearer"></div>

</div>
</div>







